Package: geoidep
Type: Package
Title: Download Geographic Data on Various Topics Provided and Managed by the Spatial Data Infrastructure of Peru
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
 c(person(given = "antony", family = "barja",email = "geografo.pe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5921-2858"))
           )
Description: Provides R users with easy access to official cartographic data from Peru on a range of topics,
  including society, transport, environment, agriculture, urban and rural cadastral information, and climate.
  It also includes data from regional government entities and technical-scientific institutions,
  all managed by the Spatial Data Infrastructure of Peru.
